  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this single-site, randomized, controlled and double-blind clinical trial, the
      investigators evaluate the effect of sodium bicarbonate on prevention of acute kidney injury
      in high risk patients undergoing off pump coronary bypass surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
