  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>compare the incidence of acute kidney injury</measure>
    <time_frame>Change of Indexes of renal function including SCr, cystatin C, creatinine clearance from 24 hrs before operation to postoperative day (POD) 5.</time_frame>
    <description>The diagnostic criteria for AKI is followed by AKIN criteria (absolutely increase in the SCr concentration ≥ 0.3 mg/dL from baseline, ≥ 50% increase in the SCr concentration within 48 hours after operation).</description>
  </primary_outcome>
